# Preventive hygiene — secret patterns to never read. Defense in depth.
#
# ⚠️ NOT enforced by the Claude Code harness (verified 2026-05-28). The
# real read-block lives in `.claude/settings.json` under `permissions.deny`
# ("Read(...)"). This file is kept as intent documentation + a net for any
# third-party tool that honors it.
#
# None of these files exist in the repo today (no secrets by construction),
# but they are listed to prevent accidental reads if a future contributor
# adds one.

# Variables d'environnement
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Certificats et clés
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.pfx

# Identités SSH (au cas où le repo serait cloné dans un dossier qui en contient)
id_rsa
id_rsa.*
id_ed25519
id_ed25519.*

# Secrets / credentials génériques
secrets/
**/credentials*
**/auth.json
